<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- وَثَقْبُ أُذُنِ صَبِيٍّ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَيَجِبُ خِتَانُ ذَكَرٍ وَأُنْثَى بُعَيْدَ بُلُوغٍ مَعَ أَمْنِ الضَّرَرِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيُسَنُّ:</span> قَبْلَهُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيُكْرَهُ:</span> سَابِعَ وِلَادَتِهِ، وَمِنْهَا إِلَيْهِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span class="c5"> فُرُوضُ الوُضُوءِ سِتَّةٌ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> غَسْلُ الوَجْهِ <span class="c2">(١)</span>، مَعَ مَضْمَضَةٍ وَاسْتِنْشَاقٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَغَسْلُ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> اليَدَيْنِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَالرِّجْلَيْنِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[٤]</span> وَمَسْحُ جَمِيعِ الرَّأْسِ، مَعَ <span class="c2">(٣)</span> الأُذُنَيْنِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
